---
// Faithful port of aminezegmou.com Loader (Vue/Nuxt) → vanilla JS + GSAP.
// 4 timelines: intro (draw) → progress (random steps) → complete (ready state)
// → exit (on click). Hover scales circles. CommandOSS palette + "C" logo.
---

<div class="cmdoss-loader" data-loader>
  <div class="cmdoss-loader__bg" data-bg></div>

  <!-- Ambient technical layer (decorative, non-interactive) -->
